Enhance system reliability and ensure seamless integration across critical modules by addressing synchronization, lifecycle alignment (EOL/EOVS), and performance inconsistencies.

Scope Includes:

Stabilization of legacy and newly integrated modules

Resolution of VA rendering and sync-related issues

Ensuring EOL/EOVS module behavior aligns with platform standards

Refactoring for better maintainability and performance

Regression validation and system-wide impact checks

Expected Outcomes:

Improved modular sync and consistency

Reduced production issues related to lifecycle & legacy modules

Streamlined platform behavior across subsystems

